This is a simple theme for OSQA.

This theme was tested on Google Chrome Beta 10.0.648.114 and 
Firefox 3.6.13 with OSQA Dev Build 775.

Installation instructions:

Assuming you already have osqa installed into a folder named osqa-server:

    cd osqa-server/forum/skins
    git clone git://github.com/kristi/OSQA_Simplton.git OSQA_Simplton
    cd ../..
    vim settings_local.py

Now in settings_local.py, change the value for OSQA_DEFAULT_SKIN:

    OSQA_DEFAULT_SKIN = 'OSQA_Simplton'

Enjoy.

====

Updating existing theme from repository

    cd osqa-server/forum/skins/OSQA_Simplton
    git pull

====

Uninstalling

    cd osqa-server
    rm -rf forum/skins/OSQA_Simplton
    vim settings_local.py

Change OSQA_DEFAULT_SKIN back to 'default'
